<div class="thumbinner" style="width:167px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Phineas_gage_-_1868_skull_diagram.jpg" class="image" title="&quot;Front and lateral view of the cranium, representing the direction in which the iron traversed its cavity...&quot; [1]"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/28/Phineas_gage_-_1868_skull_diagram.jpg" width="165" height="234" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Phineas_gage_-_1868_skull_diagram.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
"<i>Front and lateral view of the cranium, representing the direction in which the iron traversed its cavity...</i>" <sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></div>
</div>
</div>
