<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFMacmillan.2C_M._.282008.29">Macmillan, M. (2008). <a href="http://www.thepsychologist.org.uk/archive/archive_home.cfm/volumeID_21-editionID_164-ArticleID_1399-getfile_getPDF/thepsychologist%5C0908look.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.thepsychologist.org.uk/archive/archive_home.cfm/volumeID_21-editionID_164-ArticleID_1399-getfile_getPDF/thepsychologist%5C0908look.pdf" rel="nofollow">"Phineas Gage – Unravelling the myth <i>The Psychologist</i> (</a><a href="/wiki/British_Psychological_Society" title="British Psychological Society">British Psychological Society</a>), 21(9): 828-831"<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.thepsychologist.org.uk/archive/archive_home.cfm/volumeID_21-editionID_164-ArticleID_1399-getfile_getPDF/thepsychologist%5C0908look.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.thepsychologist.org.uk/archive/archive_home.cfm/volumeID_21-editionID_164-ArticleID_1399-getfile_getPDF/thepsychologist%5C0908look.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.thepsychologist.org.uk/archive/archive_home.cfm/volumeID_21-editionID_164-ArticleID_1399-getfile_getPDF/thepsychologist%5C0908look.pdf</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Phineas+Gage+%E2%80%93+Unravelling+the+myth+%27%27The+Psychologist%27%27+%28%5B%5BBritish+Psychological+Society%5D%5D%29%2C+21%289%29%3A+828-831&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Macmillan%2C+M.+%282008%29&amp;rft.au=Macmillan%2C+M.+%282008%29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thepsychologist.org.uk%2Farchive%2Farchive_home.cfm%2FvolumeID_21-editionID_164-ArticleID_1399-getfile_getPDF%2Fthepsychologist%255C0908look.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Phineas_Gage"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
