<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Phineas_Gage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFJohn_Fleischman2002">John Fleischman (2002). <i>Phineas Gage: A Gruesome but True Story About Brain Science</i>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0618052526" class="internal">ISBN 0-618-05252-6</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Phineas+Gage%3A+A+Gruesome+but+True+Story+About+Brain+Science&amp;rft.aulast=John+Fleischman&amp;rft.au=John+Fleischman&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.isbn=0-618-05252-6&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Phineas_Gage"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> (Aimed at middle-school students)</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFKelley_DJ.2C_Farhoud_M.2C_Meyerand_ME.2C_Nelson_DL.2C_Ramirez_LF.2C_et_al.2007">Kelley DJ, Farhoud M, Meyerand ME, Nelson DL, Ramirez LF, et al. (2007). "Creating Physical 3D Stereolithograph Models of Brain and Skull". <i><a href="/wiki/PLoS_ONE" title="PLoS ONE">PLoS ONE</a></i> <b>2</b> (10): e1119. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0001119" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0001119" rel="nofollow">10.1371/journal.pone.0001119</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Creating+Physical+3D+Stereolithograph+Models+of+Brain+and+Skull&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BPLoS+ONE%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Kelley+DJ%2C+Farhoud+M%2C+Meyerand+ME%2C+Nelson+DL%2C+Ramirez+LF%2C+et+al.&amp;rft.au=Kelley+DJ%2C+Farhoud+M%2C+Meyerand+ME%2C+Nelson+DL%2C+Ramirez+LF%2C+et+al.&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.volume=2&amp;rft.issue=10&amp;rft.pages=e1119&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0001119&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Phineas_Gage"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
